arguments.template:
<ion-button fivCenter (click)="onClick()">
  <fiv-icon slot="icon-only" [name]="icon"></fiv-icon>
</ion-button>

<!-- TODO if value is empty label or title can not be clicked, show placeholder?! -->
<ion-title *ngIf="type === 'title' && !editing" (click)="edit()" (@titleAnim.done)="titleAnimDone($event)" [@titleAnim]>
    {{value}}</ion-title>
<ion-label *ngIf="type === 'label' && !editing" class="label" (click)="edit()" (@titleAnim.done)="titleAnimDone($event)" [@titleAnim]>
    {{value}}</ion-label>
<ion-input *ngIf="editing" [(ngModel)]="internalValue" (blur)="onBlur()" (keyup.enter)="onEnterClick()"
    (keyup.escape)="onEscapeClick()" #input [@titleAnim] [ngClass]="{'title-input': type === 'title'}">
</ion-input>
<ion-icon class="indicator" [ngClass]="{'rotate': expandable.isOpen}" [name]="icon"></ion-icon>
{{hintText}}

arguments.template:
<ion-item [color]="color" [disabled]="disabled" [lines]="lines">
  <ion-label *ngIf="placeholder" [position]="position">{{ placeholder }}</ion-label>
  <ion-input [type]="show ? 'text' : 'password'" [(ngModel)]="passwordValue" [clearOnEdit]="clearOnEdit"
    (ionBlur)="blur()"></ion-input>
  <ion-icon slot="end" [name]="show ? hideIcon : showIcon" (click)="toggleShowPassword()"></ion-icon>
</ion-item>
{{text}}

<ng-template>
  <ng-content></ng-content>
</ng-template>

{{title}}
{{subtitle}}
{{index}}

{{i + 1}}
{{content.title}}
{{content.subtitle}}

<ion-toolbar [@searchbarAnim]="{value:state, params: {width: smallWidth}}"
  (@searchbarAnim.done)="searchBarStateChange($event)" [color]="color" [ngClass]="{'small': state === 'small'}">
  <ion-buttons slot="start">
    <ng-content select="[start]"></ng-content>

  </ion-buttons>
  <ion-title [@titleAnim] *ngIf="titleVisible && state !== 'small'">{{title}}</ion-title>
  <ion-input (ionChange)="fivInputChange.emit($event)" [placeholder]="!titleVisible ? placeholder : ''" autofocus #input
    class="toolbar-searchbar" [@titleAnim] (@titleAnim.done)="seachbarAnimDone($event,input)" *ngIf="searching">
  </ion-input>

  <ion-buttons slot="end">
    <ion-button (click)="toggleSearchbar()">
      <fiv-icon [name]="searching ? 'md-close' : 'md-search'"></fiv-icon>
    </ion-button>
    <ng-content select="[end]"></ng-content>

  </ion-buttons>
</ion-toolbar>

<ng-template>
  <ng-content></ng-content>
</ng-template>

<fiv-ripple (fivClick)="onClick()" class="tab" [ngClass]="{'active': active}">
  <fiv-icon [(indicatorValue)]="badge" [name]="icon"></fiv-icon>
  <ion-label>{{name}}</ion-label>
</fiv-ripple>

<ion-buttons *ngIf="buttons" [slot]="slot">

  <fiv-button [color]="color" *ngIf="(slot === 'start' || slot ==='primary') && count < buttons.length && text"
    (click)="onMenuClicked($event)" [text]="text"></fiv-button>

  <fiv-button [color]="color" *ngIf="(slot === 'start' || slot ==='primary') && count < buttons.length && !text"
    (click)="onMenuClicked($event)" [icon]="'md-more'"></fiv-button>
  <ng-container *ngIf="iconsOnly">
    <fiv-button [color]="button.color" (click)="onButtonClicked(i)" [icon]="button.icon"
      *ngFor="let button of buttons.toArray() | slice:0:count; let i = index;"></fiv-button>
  </ng-container>
  <ng-container *ngIf="!iconsOnly">
    <fiv-button [color]="button.color" (click)="onButtonClicked(i)" [icon]="button.icon" [text]="button.text"
      *ngFor="let button of buttons.toArray() | slice:0:count; let i = index;"></fiv-button>
  </ng-container>
  <fiv-button [color]="color" *ngIf="(slot === 'end' || slot ==='secondary') && count < buttons.length && !text"
    (click)="onMenuClicked($event)" [icon]="icon"></fiv-button>
  <fiv-button [color]="color" *ngIf="(slot === 'end' || slot ==='secondary') && count < buttons.length && text"
    (click)="onMenuClicked($event)" [text]="text"></fiv-button>
</ion-buttons>

<ion-button [color]="color" [disabled]="disabled">
  <fiv-icon [name]="icon"></fiv-icon>
  {{text}}
</ion-button>

<ion-chip [@status] (click)="FivNetworkStatusClicked()" *ngIf="visible">
  <fiv-icon [indicatorValue]="-1" [fivCenter] [off]="status === 'offline'" name="cloud"></fiv-icon>
</ion-chip>

<ion-button (click)="buttonClick()">
  <fiv-icon [color]="color" [name]="icon"></fiv-icon>
</ion-button>
{{indicatorValue}} 9+

<svg [style.width.px]="diameter" [style.height.px]="diameter" [attr.viewBox]="viewBox"
  preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" focusable="false" [ngSwitch]="mode == 'indeterminate'">
  <circle [attr.stroke]="_color" *ngSwitchCase="true" cx="50%" cy="50%" [attr.r]="circleRadius"
    [style.animation-name]="'fiv-progress-spinner-stroke-rotate-' + diameter"
    [style.stroke-dashoffset.px]="strokeDashOffset" [style.stroke-dasharray.px]="strokeCircumference"
    [style.stroke-width.%]="circleStrokeWidth"></circle>

  <circle [attr.stroke]="_color" class="determinate-circle" #determinateCircle *ngSwitchCase="false" cx="50%" cy="50%"
    [attr.r]="circleRadius" [style.stroke-dashoffset.px]="strokeDashOffset"
    [style.stroke-dasharray.px]="strokeCircumference" [style.stroke-width.%]="circleStrokeWidth"></circle>
</svg>

<ng-template #content>
  <ng-content></ng-content>
</ng-template>
<ng-content #content></ng-content>

<ng-template #ref>
  <ng-content></ng-content>

<ion-toolbar color="transparent">
  <ion-buttons slot="start">
    <ion-button (click)="gallery.close()">
      <ion-icon slot="icon-only" name="close"></ion-icon>
    </ion-button>
  </ion-buttons>
  <ion-buttons slot="end">
    <ion-button (click)="gallery.fullscreen()">
      <fiv-icon slot="icon-only" [name]="gallery.inFullscreen ? 'contract': 'expand'"></fiv-icon>
    </ion-button>
    <ion-button (click)="gallery.zoom()">
      <fiv-icon slot="icon-only" [name]="gallery.zoomedIn ? 'remove': 'add'"></fiv-icon>
    </ion-button>
  </ion-buttons>
</ion-toolbar>
